<p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>早在2021年，Buckley就进行了<em>NME的《</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-interviews/james-buckley-soundtrack-of-my-life-inbetweeners-2884624">我一生》采访的配乐</a>，并透露他去过的第一次演出是2002年在Finsbury Park的Oasis。</p><p> “支持令人难以置信： <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-charlatans" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Charlatans</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-rebel-motorcycle-club" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Black Rebel Motorcycle Club</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cornershop" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cornershop</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-coral" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Coral</a> ……感觉就像那天有30个乐队演奏。大门在中午，我当时就像：&#39;我一定要在那里，我不想想念Oasis！&#39;&#39;</p><p> “我以为这就是演出的感觉。那天晚上，绿洲是世界上最伟大的乐队。看着他们现场演奏，这完全是有道理的。有时是一个团圆吗？我想如果<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Stone-Roses">石玫瑰</a>团聚了几场演出，那么任何乐队都可以。”</p><p>现在，聚会是现实， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-line-up-band-reunion-tour-members-2025-3845348"><em>NME</em>与即将到来的巡回演出的消息来源进行了交谈，并揭示了谁将参加乐队阵容的细节</a>。他们说，安迪·贝尔（Andy Bell）将在吉他上乘坐低音，宝石Archer和Paul“ Bonehead” Arthurs，而Joey Waronker则将在鼓上。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/comic-relief-is-teasing-something-oasis-related-for-the-2025-red-nose-day-show-3846552"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>乐队被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-new-order-the-white-stripes-mariah-carey-lead-nominations-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-2025-3837368">提名为今年的摇滚名人堂，</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/New-Order">新的订单</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-White-Stripes">白色条纹</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Mariah-Carey">玛丽亚·凯里（Mariah Carey）</a>之类的乐队，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-is-for-wankers-after-oasis-nominated-3837513">利亚姆（Liam）继续坚持认为这一荣誉是“为wankers”</a> 。</p></div></div><p>邮<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-inbetweeners-stars-james-buckley-and-joe-thomas-parody-oasis-liam-and-noel-gallagher-in-comic-relief-sketch-3848380">报的《 Inbetweeners》明星James Buckley和Joe Thomas Parody Oasis的Liam和Noel Gallagher在漫画浮雕素描中</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Yungblud在亲密惊喜Scala Show上首次亮相三首新歌https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-debuts-three-new-new-new-songs-at-in--in--in--in--in-sirprise-scla-scala-show-3848376?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = yungblud-debuts-three-three-new-new-songs-s in tim-Scalprise-scala-showPoppy Burton Sat, 22 Mar 2025 08:41:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3848376 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Yungblud" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “回来真是太好了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-debuts-three-new-songs-at-intimate-surprise-scala-show-3848376">Yungblud帖子在Intimate Scala Show上首次出现</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现在NME上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Yungblud" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yungblud">Yungblud</a>昨晚（3月21日）在他亲密的惊喜Scala节目中首次发行了三首新歌。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-interview-bludfest-2-line-up-tickets-new-double-album-3822568">Yungblud告诉我们有关Bludfest 2和“他妈的Bonkers”的新专辑：“这是总体规划”</a></strong></li></ul><p>伦敦亲密的演出是在歌手（真实的名字多米尼克·哈里森（Dominic Harrison））以单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-shares-epic-self-reclaiming-new-single-hello-heaven-hello-3847332">Hello Heaven，Hello&#39;&#39;</a>的形式分享了他2025年的第一首新音乐，这是他自2024年以来的“崩溃”以来的第一首歌，也是他自2022年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/yungblud-yungblud-review-3302420">自名字自名字专辑</a>以来的首张LP。</p><p>本周早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-announces-free-show-in-london-featuring-songs-from-his-upcoming-new-album-3847658">他分享了音乐会的消息</a>，告诉歌迷他将“演奏新专辑中的几首歌”。昨晚，他从“ Hello Heaven，Hello”开始了四首歌的名单 - 后来送上<a href="https://x.com/yungblud/status/1903130779137302630" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X/Twitter</a> ，说出对歌曲“ Feel Like Magic”的反应。</p><p>他在国王十字架场地向人群讲话时说：“回来真是太好了。”在进入Brit-Pop启发的“ Lovesick Lullaby”之前。</p><p>从那里开始，他将“僵尸”的现场亮相进行了首次亮相，并用“鬼魂”绕开了场景，在此之前，他敦促人群在此刻享用。 “伦敦，我可以帮你一个恩吗？”他说。 “每个人都可以把他们的电话放开吗？这首歌是关于理解您的死亡率，因为我们很久没有在这里他妈的……别忘了他妈的活着的人。” </p><div id="playlist-player-jwplayer"><div class="playlist-player-container"><figure id="attachment_3848382" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3848382" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3848382" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1.jpg" alt="Yungblud" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-yungblud-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3848382" class="wp-caption-text"> Yungblud将于3月21日星期五在伦敦的Scala现场表演。信贷：Tom Pallant</figcaption></figure></div></div><h3> <strong>Yungblud在Scala播放：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1  - “你好天堂，你好&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2  - “ lovesick lullaby&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>3  - “僵尸”</strong><br /> <strong>4  - 鬼</strong></p><p>目前，尽管Yungblud在最近几个月中一直在删除许多提示，但对他即将发行的专辑的了解鲜为人知。去年12月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-interview-bludfest-2-line-up-tickets-new-double-album-3822568">他告诉<em>NME</em> ，这很可能是一张双专辑</a>，他还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-shares-thoughts-on-his-upcoming-album-i-have-never-felt-more-clear-3846583">讨论了自己对唱片的骄傲</a>，并通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-teases-next-era-as-he-returns-to-social-media-with-new-look-hello-3845689">重返社交媒体来</a>使粉丝说话。</p><p>最近，哈里森（Harrison）与<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-zane-lowe-show/id1704203180" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple Music</a>进行了交谈，并分享了有关制作唱片的更多细节。这涉及推动粉丝可以期望的东西，并从摇滚乐中的一些知名人士那里汲取灵感。</p><p>他说：“我一直在听很多古老的学校音乐，回到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bonnie-raitt">邦妮·莱特（Bonnie Raitt）</a>和琳达·朗斯塔特（Linda Ronstadt）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">莱德·齐柏林（Led Zeppelin）</a>等人，甚至还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）</a> 。” “摇滚是我的流派。我觉得我一直在涉足许多不同的事情并试图扭曲摇滚，但是我觉得那一刻令人兴奋，因为摇滚音乐感觉是球形的……它听起来很大，听起来很像电影。” </p><figure id="attachment_3822605" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3822605" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3822605" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/yungblud_bludfest_interview_3.jpg" alt="Yungblud在2024年6月21日在Landgraaf举行的PinkPop音乐节的第一天演出。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/yungblud_bludfest_interview_3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/yungblud_bludfest_interview_3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/yungblud_bludfest_interview_3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/yungblud_bludfest_interview_3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/yungblud_bludfest_interview_3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/yungblud_bludfest_interview_3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3822605" class="wp-caption-text"> Yungblud在2024年6月21日在Landgraaf举行的PinkPop音乐节的第一天演出。</figcaption></figure><p>他还继续分享自己对最终结​​果的满意程度，并解释了对他的“文化重置”的感觉。</p><p>关于从LED Zeppelin Echo汲取灵感的评论Yungblud于去年3月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-new-album-interview-britpop-concept-oasis-verve-bowie-madonna-3604307">与<em>NME</em>进行了交谈，并将其</a>命名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-verve">The Verve，Verve</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/primal-scream">Primal Scream</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/MY-CHEMICAL-ROMANCE">My Chemical Romance</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">David Bowie</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">Madonna作为灵感</a>。</p><p>哈里森指出，唱片的咒语将是：“彼此聚在一起，互相看，成为人类”，而对面说：“操你，这是我们必须实现的世界。”</p><p>在谈到概念专辑的想法时，他继续说：“这是&#39;tommy&#39;，这是一个&#39;四季度&#39;[ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-WHO">who</a> ]。这是&#39;opera on the opera&#39;&#39;[queen&#39;[queen]。这是一个&#39;黑人游行&#39;[<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/MY-CHEMICAL-ROMANCE">我的化学浪漫</a>&#39;。这是“城市赞美诗”。 前。</p><p>在其他Yungblud新闻中，今年夏天，Doncaster歌手将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-announces-bigger-and-better-bludfest-2025-get-ready-buy-tickets-3822031">他自己的节日的第二部分Bludfest</a>演出，该节目还将看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chase-atlantic">Chase Atlantic</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/DENZEL-CURRY">Denzel Curry</a> ，Blackbear， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackbear">Blackbear</a>和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover">NME Cover Cover Stars</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/RACHEL-CHINOURIRI">Rachel Chinouriri</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peach-prc">Peach Prc的</a>露面。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fyungblud-tickets%2Fartist%2F5238519" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>的门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-debuts-three-new-songs-at-intimate-surprise-scala-show-3848376">Yungblud帖子在Intimate Scala Show上首次出现</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现在NME上。</p> ;
